to use docker-compose...

1.put docker file, Jar and docker.compose.yml in one folder. (src/main/docker)
2. open terminal from the above folder.
3. sudo snap start docker - to start the docker(if yiu have installed docker using snap)
4. sudo docker-compose up
5. Optional - if you want to re run again after changing the source code- follow below steps
6. Ctrl +C in the terminal
7. sudo docker-compose down - to stop the docker
8. sudo docker images -  to display the images
9. sudo docker rmi <image_name> = to remove the image
10.copy the latest jar to the main/docker folder
11.sudo docker-compose up - to start again